The paper discusses the risks associated with uncontrolled financial spreadsheets and the need for organizations to automate their internal controls over critical spreadsheets. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), software engineering (cs.SE), databases (cs.DB), cybersecurity (cs.CYBER), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as these categories are closely related to the issues discussed in the paper.
